						               													<description>Alteration is a post apocalyptic card game set in a science fantasy futuristic world that has been destroyed by the cataclysm known as The Great War. In Alteration players take on the roles of mutants, plants, animals, and even pure strain humans in a struggle to claim powerful technology left from before the great war! players take turns acquiring new mutations and researching technology to defeat the opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Alteration each player receives a random character card that they will use to get their stats, hit points, and special abilities. Each turn players will chose different actions to get more mutation cards, try to research technology, Attack an opponent, or use a power on one of there cards. many of these actions use dice to determine if the attack or power hits or if you can repair the tech you are trying to use and gain its card for use next turn. play continues until only one player has hit points left. The last mutant standing is the winner!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you have what it takes to traverse the irradiated wastes of Alteration?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
